hwr = wthr.HourlyWeatherReport(lat=self.lat, lon=self.lon, date=self.day,
    time=self.time)
self.session.add(hwr)
self.session.commit()
report = wthr.weather_report((self.lat, self.lon, self.day), kwargs=self.
    cache_kwargs)
self.assertTrue(report is not None)
self.assertTrue(isinstance(report, dict))
self.assertTrue(all(k in ['report', 'hits', 'misses'] for k in report.keys()))
self.assertTrue(isinstance(report.get('report'), pd.DataFrame))
self.assertTrue(report.get('report').shape is not (0, 0))
responses.activate
